snippet.title: Warhawk PSX/PS1 Gameplay Trailer [ウォーホーク PS1版]
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer of flight action game "Warhawk" (PS1/PSX). PS3 version  might be remake of this game. This movie is captured from Japanese version, and this game is known as "Air Assault" in Japan.

PS1用のフライトシューティング「ウォーホーク (邦題：エア・アサルト)」
